data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. the seller is highly motivated and is offering a generous seller concession of $10,000 toward buyer's closing cost and buydown rate. Home located in excellent comunity with NO CDD! Open concept home build in 2015 with 4 bedrooms, 2 baths, living room and dinning room combo. You will be impressed with the spacious kitchen with eating space in the island and closet pantry. The comfortable master bedroom is located in the back of the home with amazing view of the tropical landscaping from the double windows. This suite has a walk-in closet and bathroom with two sink, shower stall with separate tub and separate toilet. The second bathroom has two sinks and tub with shower. The huge fenced patio with 12.5 feet in both side (25 feet between neighbors) of the property and cover lanai space will give you the opportunity to enjoy with your family the excellent weather of Florida. The property has ceiling fans, epoxy and opener in garage, fruit trees and irrigation system. Lot size 65' x 120' with conservation area in the back. Great Opportunity to join this exquisite area located minutes away from 192  for easy access to turnpike, restaurants, farmacies, hospital, medical offices, mall and supermarkets.
